{"id": "ChIJVwLhg12HhYARcIdFDox3HxM", "rating": 4.4, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 2604, "displayName": {"text": "San Tung", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Famed dry fried chicken wings, handmade noodles & other Chinese eats in a no-frills setting.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJVwLhg12HhYARcIdFDox3HxM/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pOR01WSmpTSFF4YW1OMWRIcHBVbU42VWtoQlEwRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 weeks ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "The San Tung Chinese restaurant sure smacks out some amazing Char Siu Chicken, and the Potsickers were simply amazing!  This restaurant is far underrated, my old pal Albino Bob raved about it so much...I just had to go!  It was well worth the trip across the bridge!  5 ☆☆☆☆☆'s all day long!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The San Tung Chinese restaurant sure smacks out some amazing Char Siu Chicken, and the Potsickers were simply amazing!  This restaurant is far underrated, my old pal Albino Bob raved about it so much...I just had to go!  It was well worth the trip across the bridge!  5 ☆☆☆☆☆'s all day long!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "American Angler", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110528677426487009216/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWCYctkW9WSngtVdHYS7nmmTl4RYD8TmmC6-BvvxZeU6DwBbO-8=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba7"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-18T16:57:48.928233069Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pOR01WSmpTSFF4YW1OMWRIcHBVbU42VWtoQlEwRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pOR01WSmpTSFF4YW1OMWRIcHBVbU42VWtoQlEwRRAB!2m1!1s0x8085875d83e10257:0x131f778c0e458770"}, {"name": "places/ChIJVwLhg12HhYARcIdFDox3HxM/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pGVlQxVkJUblUwY1VaV2IxUldVbmw1VUVac1NVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "7 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "It's packed and it may take bit to be seated. You write your name and party size on the white board.\n\nThe dry fried chicken wings are the best chicken wings I've had. Juicy and crunchy with a nice sweet glaze. The green beans, dry black bean sauce noodles, and hot braised chicken were all good but the dry fried chicken wings were the standout!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "It's packed and it may take bit to be seated. You write your name and party size on the white board.\n\nThe dry fried chicken wings are the best chicken wings I've had. Juicy and crunchy with a nice sweet glaze. The green beans, dry black bean sauce noodles, and hot braised chicken were all good but the dry fried chicken wings were the standout!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "WAB", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100252936989050254140/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4fyMmNf5KOU8IZWvOShA3ktMALRBpyCwYhmrS4ySXurbTm2zg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-11-17T20:49:46.503957065Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pGVlQxVkJUblUwY1VaV2IxUldVbmw1VUVac1NVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pGVlQxVkJUblUwY1VaV2IxUldVbmw1VUVac1NVRRAB!2m1!1s0x8085875d83e10257:0x131f778c0e458770"}, {"name": "places/ChIJVwLhg12HhYARcIdFDox3HxM/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21sMmEweHVObWRIUWpOb1gzQkNPRU5YY2xsR2NIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 3, "text": {"text": "We ordered two small soups and the fried chicken wings.\n\n🍲 Tomato Soup and Egg Drop Soup: For a small, they were quite generous with the portion size. Definitely could have ordered one to share. Both were flavored quite well and enjoyable.\n\n🍗 San Tung Fried Chicken: I heard the fried chicken was a must-try, but it wasn’t for me. It was far too sweet for me and just reminded me of korean fried chicken. I don’t prefer my protein on the sweet side, and these left a jarring sweet aftertaste in my mouth I did not enjoy. I will not be back for the wings but would be interested in other things.\n\nThe prices appear to be a bit more expensive for Chinese food, but the portion sizes are slightly larger than average.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "We ordered two small soups and the fried chicken wings.\n\n🍲 Tomato Soup and Egg Drop Soup: For a small, they were quite generous with the portion size. Definitely could have ordered one to share. Both were flavored quite well and enjoyable.\n\n🍗 San Tung Fried Chicken: I heard the fried chicken was a must-try, but it wasn’t for me. It was far too sweet for me and just reminded me of korean fried chicken. I don’t prefer my protein on the sweet side, and these left a jarring sweet aftertaste in my mouth I did not enjoy. I will not be back for the wings but would be interested in other things.\n\nThe prices appear to be a bit more expensive for Chinese food, but the portion sizes are slightly larger than average.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Anjera C", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108522339205447123364/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXg40zwP6d7Uiq0m1N4s1w3xYR42SWNsGgcIDQUHV67wR7RLo8=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-02T01:18:02.310619650Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21sMmEweHVObWRIUWpOb1gzQkNPRU5YY2xsR2NIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21sMmEweHVObWRIUWpOb1gzQkNPRU5YY2xsR2NIYxAB!2m1!1s0x8085875d83e10257:0x131f778c0e458770"}, {"name": "places/ChIJVwLhg12HhYARcIdFDox3HxM/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xFMFJVNTVhMmhrT0dSSVltWjJWMEZ6YVhOc1ZXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Came on a Sunday night and there was a long line. The wait is well worth it. Definitely one of the most delicious Chinese restaurants in the bay area. The wings are a must as it has a reputation for being the best. All the other dishes we ordered were also so good, we loved everything! A favorite at the table was the Cherry pork which is very tasty and was pretty comparable to the chicken wings. The dry black bean noodles is also a must but overall everything was delicious and you can’t go wrong with anything on the menu.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Came on a Sunday night and there was a long line. The wait is well worth it. Definitely one of the most delicious Chinese restaurants in the bay area. The wings are a must as it has a reputation for being the best. All the other dishes we ordered were also so good, we loved everything! A favorite at the table was the Cherry pork which is very tasty and was pretty comparable to the chicken wings. The dry black bean noodles is also a must but overall everything was delicious and you can’t go wrong with anything on the menu.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Amy Le", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100246001259258271020/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJWIz7VPFiC3z_raN19qLpcVoWGVteVL9tpc9XWkU1kyNs5cQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-19T19:24:29.075420612Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xFMFJVNTVhMmhrT0dSSVltWjJWMEZ6YVhOc1ZXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xFMFJVNTVhMmhrT0dSSVltWjJWMEZ6YVhOc1ZXYxAB!2m1!1s0x8085875d83e10257:0x131f778c0e458770"}, {"name": "places/ChIJVwLhg12HhYARcIdFDox3HxM/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tWME9EY3laVVpmZW1VM1ZWaENVVlJRTTJkQ2JIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "One of the best Chinese food in San Francisco. They are known for this amazing chicken wings. Their sticky and salt & pepper chicken wings are very special. Delicious food all around. Very busy place from the moment they open for business so plan accordingly and expect 10 to 30 minutes wait.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "One of the best Chinese food in San Francisco. They are known for this amazing chicken wings. Their sticky and salt & pepper chicken wings are very special. Delicious food all around. Very busy place from the moment they open for business so plan accordingly and expect 10 to 30 minutes wait.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Essam Abdelazim", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106439830925271918938/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU2rYKV2vKFh_Qva8Tf4kEABLBpSyo_WRzWQB3bB2x4JDaKG3z-=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-25T06:15:23.711796142Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tWME9EY3laVVpmZW1VM1ZWaENVVlJRTTJkQ2JIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tWME9EY3laVVpmZW1VM1ZWaENVVlJRTTJkQ2JIYxAB!2m1!1s0x8085875d83e10257:0x131f778c0e458770"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJVwLhg12HhYARcIdFDox3HxM/photos/AWCwydgHaOfUSsiJ1TBBo5J6oKEX-KHaKrx2fHR7HUvt-RpKf6D8juhBpPgLyV4it94-ffDyDCqo0moY3BTeXUMOZRo91quUcK251qx0O7If8_XO11MsjLztGRfCTYfaLXOUeMVGxeQ_OGnAGqdneBn5WYLiHIJed4T1LNNufifCYHgQ6Rr4paPQ39l450hv0ykkhFwFlDsAM8gxSKUMs7H6Uo5YFKOUrUs7hDXPD4a2CmQEcbhatFifUhx04vrOT6UNmkO_yK3puF_IDwB3_iqJg2J-kM5YVQIMQapGv2Kcs7y8lat-0pV6Af_h38MycNQupOM-gb9JNrVE5U6LEbES91rV-vTCXmMQAxZqbyYUd8-t07HI45GMHKdAIjfPFs0v3uP6y1P3uRo-nEoF2DIP5ijmSeBB12nDiBsUUrtd5kAd4sTnQp6BFIsRUutkvw", "widthPx": 4800, "heightPx": 3600, "a